metadata.name: The Trinity
metadata.description:
These three Blaque Angel heads represent the cyclical nature of our existence from birth, preservation & regeneration.

This is a 1/1 art piece from an exclusive upcoming collection set to drop in 2022. 

The collector will receive an additional art piece representing her in a different format and symbol on her forehead. 

The collector will also receive a framed still version of the original art piece.
